      <p>Our D&I VR training is here to assist your organisation in ensuring you get the best out of your people.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="module-info">
      <div class="module-pros">
        <h5>MITIGATING BIAS AND STEREOTYPES</h5>
        <%= image_tag "d&i-1" %>
        <p>Diversity and inclusion training addresses unconscious biases, fostering fair treatment and reducing discrimination. Employees learn to recognise and challenge biases that may affect teamwork and creativity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="module-pros">
        <h5>BEHAVIOURAL <br> CHANGE</h5>
        <%= image_tag "d&i-2" %>
