      </div>
      <div class="module-pros">
        <h5>CULTIVATING INCLUSIVE MINDSETS</h5>
        <%= image_tag "d&i-3" %>
        <p>Diversity and inclusion training promote awareness and understanding of various backgrounds, perspectives, and experiences. Employees develop inclusive mindsets that enrich collaboration and decision-making.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
